	v_max (m/s)	7.777761
	v_min (km/h)	0.000119
	v_min (m/s)	0.000033

```

**Input files:**
[groundtruth2.txt](https://github.com/MichaelGrupp/evo/files/2168680/groundtruth2.txt) - position from GPS converted to NED
[interpolate_ned_output_linear_cut.txt](https://github.com/MichaelGrupp/evo/files/2168682/interpolate_ned_output_linear_cut.txt) - position from IMU (NED)
both are gathered from the Pixhawk.


