2830,IssuesEvent,2018-01-05 20:06:36+00:00,5598737,BurntSushi/nflgame,2996205,ochawkeye,,,opened,Post Season PSA,[],[],0,"Just a reminder.

If you want your schedule to update, you'll need to have [`nflgame\live.py\_CUR_SCHEDULE`](https://github.com/BurntSushi/nflgame/blob/master/nflgame/live.py#L73) point to the postseason xml URL.

