3631,IssuesEvent,2017-05-15 22:36:14+00:00,29050338,mementum/backtrader,5713511,mementum,,,closed,Limit order is not getting executed,[],[],3,"| Problem            	| Bracket Buy order does not get executed                                                                                           	|
|--------------------	|-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------	|
| Symbol             	| 000001.SS                                                                                                                     	|
| Source Data        	| YahooFinance                                                                                                                  	|
| Backtrader-Version 	| 1.9.47.116                                                                                                                    	|
| Timeframe          	| Daily                                                                                                                         	|
| Date of occurrence 	| 2014-07-23                                                                                                                    	|
| Goal               	| Buy Bracket (Order.Limit) with buy_price over current candle|
| Expected behaviour 	| Buy gets executed and notify_order called if price goes above buy_price (Happens on 2014-07-24)                               	|
| Current behaviour  	| Order is not getting executed                                                                                                 	|

From the [documentation](https://www.backtrader.com/docu/order-creation-execution/order-creation-execution.html#limit) 

> The price set at order creation if the data touches it, starting with the next price bar

So the test scenario looks like the following:

<img width=""842"" alt=""grafik"" src=""https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/18695252/26065837/588aca5e-3995-11e7-9027-70a4f630204f.png"">

The strategy creates a `buy bracket` on 2014-07-23:

<img width=""773"" alt=""grafik"" src=""https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/18695252/26065532/8f3115fa-3994-11e7-9512-ad557a03fd49.png"">

2014-07-24 openes higher but the order is not getting executed:

<img width=""787"" alt=""grafik"" src=""https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/18695252/26065933/aa1cf450-3995-11e7-9b87-eda815586a09.png"">

Nothing changed on 2014-07-25:

<img width=""804"" alt=""grafik"" src=""https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/18695252/26065975/c8b74550-3995-11e7-8aab-b27b348f4306.png"">
",{},{}
