4086,IssuesEvent,2018-07-04 01:19:29+00:00,70314805,kyuupichan/electrumx,3319176,kyuupichan,,,closed,High memory consumption after long uptime,[],[],1,"I'm on bitcoin (segwit) mainnet, running https://github.com/kyuupichan/electrumx/commit/0dc99d7c63f2fe8e4e6f758afddc9024a239c3ff

I have noticed that e-x is using a significant amount of RAM, currently 10.75 GiB.
