4313,IssuesEvent,2018-07-16 21:01:34+00:00,54828252,agronholm/apscheduler,34254118,Juanjoorrego,,,opened,Jobs stops being exeucted,[],[],0,"Hi there.

We have some jobs that trigger a script to run every 5 seconds (i.e. 720 GETS per hour). Unfortunately, some jobs never go from Started Execution to Executed, which means that other jobs that should be executed after it never execute. There is no error, or bug in the logs, for some reason it just doesn't stop at the time when it is supposed to (doesn't transition from Started Execution to Executed).

