8935,IssuesEvent,2017-09-07 10:54:17+00:00,30863890,frictionlessdata/tableschema-py,28537352,MuhammadAlkarouri,5912125,frictionlessdata,opened,License issue: 'rfc3987' is GPL,[],[],0,"Hi,

