9023,IssuesEvent,2016-08-21 09:59:03+00:00,16316451,GoogleCloudPlatform/gcloud-python,10431849,naveensinghal,2810941,GoogleCloudPlatform,opened,Using Google Cloud Datastore API in Python Code,[],[],0,"Hi,

I am trying to Implement Google Cloud DataStore in my Python Django Project not running on Google App Engine.

