9904,IssuesEvent,2016-09-18 00:33:08+00:00,32944298,Z3Prover/z3,3085284,NikolajBjorner,11668813,Z3Prover,closed,Segmentation Fault when Proof Production and Recursive Functions are used together,[],[],1,"I get a segmentation fault with the following minimal example problem:

