(smt.searching)
(smt.restarting :propagations 0 :decisions 0 :conflicts 0 :restart 100 :restart-outer 100 :agility 0)
Segmentation fault: 11
$ 
```
",{},{}
9914,IssuesEvent,2015-12-09 18:00:22+00:00,32944298,Z3Prover/z3,511795,delcypher,11668813,Z3Prover,opened,mk_unix_dist.py is kind of pointless,[],[],0,"The proper way to build a distributable tarball is to do something like

```
$ python scripts/mk_make.py <flags to enable bindings>
$ cd build
$ make
$ mkdir staged
$ make DESTDIR=`readlink -f staged` install
$ tar -C staged -czvf z3.tar.gz .
```

The newly added ``DESTDIR`` support makes a lot of the existing python code ``mk_unix_dist()`` a bit pointless because now creating a distributable is basically the same as doing a staged install but then tarballing the result.",{},{}
