9933,IssuesEvent,2015-12-11 17:52:19+00:00,32944298,Z3Prover/z3,10155819,wintersteiger,11668813,Z3Prover,closed,Segmentation fault during Z3.FloatingPoint.get_*bits,"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/Z3Prover/z3/labels/bug', 'name': 'bug', 'color': 'fc2929'}]",[],0,"There is a bug in Z3.FloatingPoint.get_ebits and Z3.FloatingPoint.get_sbits I stumbled
