9953,IssuesEvent,2017-01-18 08:43:13+00:00,59214089,SCIP-Interfaces/PySCIPOpt,8492578,gsagnol,19473229,SCIP-Interfaces,closed,cutting planes,[],[],2,"When I have a scip model that I have already solved,
