10134,IssuesEvent,2017-05-23 15:47:09+00:00,51040886,Azure/azure-cli,5723682,tjprescott,6844498,Azure,opened,no module found 'azure.cli' after dev_setup.py,"[{'id': 420278907, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/Azure/azure-cli/labels/Packaging', 'name': 'Packaging', 'color': 'fef2c0', 'default': False}]",[],0,"Possibly related to #3351. 

