11645,IssuesEvent,2018-07-13 13:10:57+00:00,43816051,common-workflow-language/cwltool,9433472,anowlcalledjosh,9947495,common-workflow-language,opened,Having an array of enums as input causes a crash,[],[],0,"## Expected Behavior

Input of an array of enums should behave the same way as an array of strings (as long as the input is valid anyway).

## Actual Behavior

cwltool crashes when an input is an array of enums.

## Workflow Code

`tool.cwl`:

```yaml
cwlVersion: v1.0
class: CommandLineTool
baseCommand: echo
inputs:
  args:
    type:
      - type: array
        items:
          type: enum
          symbols:
            - foo
            - bar
    inputBinding:
      position: 1
outputs: []
```

`job.yml`:

```yaml
args: [foo]
```

