12722,IssuesEvent,2017-01-05 18:05:47+00:00,58479957,juju/python-libjuju,406082,johnsca,4604548,juju,opened,Cannot ssh into units in model created by libjuju,[],[],0,"Originally reported in juju-solutions/matrix#59

