13597,IssuesEvent,2016-12-29 14:43:41+00:00,51625787,vatlab/SOS,9889312,BoPeng,20074389,vatlab,reopened,A possible ulimit issue,[],[],1,"SoS will fail if too many output is produced, for example (please create a new folder and run it there)

