15351,IssuesEvent,2017-10-10 20:39:36+00:00,40684033,mozilla/sops,415617,jvehent,131524,mozilla,closed,Consistent url to the latest release.,[],[],1,"It would be helpful if you offered a consistent url to latest compatible packages release.
