  File ""/home/niklas/python35env/lib/python3.5/site-packages/deepspeech/client.py"", line 69, in main
    assert fs == 16000, ""Only 16000Hz input WAV files are supported for now!""
AssertionError: Only 16000Hz input WAV files are supported for now!
```

It would probably be helpful if the assertion printed what it thinks the value of `fs` is.

My version as obtained via pip:

