17535,IssuesEvent,2015-05-21 23:28:01+00:00,1238348,agoragames/haigha,1441066,vitaly-krugl,47092,agoragames,opened,Can't get close_info from synchronous connection,[],[],0,"If connection fails during construction of synchronous RabbitConnection or Connection, there is no way to get the close_info.

```
def onConnectionClosed(): # no arg passed to callback, so no way to get close_info
  pass

# Here, if connection set-up/negotiation/etc. fails in the constructor, `conn` is not set up, 
# so we can't get close_info directly from the instance
conn = RabbitConnection(user=""unknownuser"", close_cb=onConnectionClosed)
```",{},{}
