17581,IssuesEvent,2018-08-15 23:00:20+00:00,88679857,biolink/ontobio,2687900,kltm,25489141,biolink,opened,Change JSON file reports during GAF parsing to support better reporting,"[{'id': 586753654, 'node_id': 'MDU6TGFiZWw1ODY3NTM2NTQ=', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/biolink/ontobio/labels/enhancement', 'name': 'enhancement', 'color': '84b6eb', 'default': True}]",[],0,"The current JSON output is lacking lacking in a few key aspects to support the reporting that we'd like to have in the GO.

