17742,IssuesEvent,2017-02-16 06:04:51+00:00,13512018,python-diamond/Diamond,3051981,shortdudey123,5668086,python-diamond,closed,diamond multiprocessing inherit signal handler,"[{'id': 488425556, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/python-diamond/Diamond/labels/status:%20fix-provided', 'name': 'status: fix-provided', 'color': '009800', 'default': False}]",[],1,"if we have collertor, that will be removed later and make diamond reload(send sigHUP), diamond will remove it pid file

Situation is identical like described here:

